text: Long Beach is a city (incorporated August 10, 1905) in Harrison County, Mississippi, USA. It is part of the Gulfport-Biloxi, Mississippi Metropolitan Statistical Area. As of the 2020 census, 16,780 people lived there. It also the home of Alphonso Campbell. ==References== ==Other websites== * City of Long Beach, MS Category:Cities in Harrison County, Mississippi Category:1905 establishments in the United States
